text: Feldis/Veulden was a municipality of the district of Hinterrhein in the canton of Graubünden in Switzerland. On 1 January 2009, the former municipalities of Feldis/Veulden, Scheid, Trans and Tumegl/Tomils merged into the new municipality of Tomils. ==References== Category:Former municipalities of Graubünden
title: Feldis/Veulden
